what is Speckit
speckit ak digital ya Ai based tool hota ha jo planning documentation task management or project ko organize krna ma madad krta ha. is ka maqsad ya hita ha k koi b ak project chahe academic ya professional samj or asan wala sreps ma cpmplete kia ja saka. 
is ma specify plan task implement jesa core features hota han.jo user k project ko asani sa manage kr saken.

concepts
1.constitution 
constitution ka mutlab hota ha project ka basic structure.ya project kia q banay ja raha ha is ki boundaries kia ho ge.ya direction deta ha kam ki limits k sath.

2.specify
specify ka mutlab hota ha cheezo ko clear define krna.yani goals or requirements kia han.or kon kon c cheezen zarori han.jb he cheez clear hote h to project banana ma asani hote ha.

3.plan
plan wo step by step tareqa hota ha jis sa project ko complete kia jaye.is ma task ko order ma rakhna time decide krna or sources ka istemal hota ha. ak acha plan kam ko asan or kamyab banata ha.

4.task
task kam ka chota hissa hota ha.hr bara kam ko chota chota hisso ma divide kia jata ha.ta kam manage ho sake.hr task ki responsibility kisi na kisi person ya system ko de jate ha.

5. implement 
implement ka mutlab hota ha plan ko amal ma lana yani jis tarha planning ki us follow krta hoa real kam krna.ya hi wo stage ha jahan idea haqeqat bun jata ha. or ap ka kawab pora hota ha.
